<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../532/6477532.xml">
York Suburban Senior High School</link></senior_high_school>
.</p>
<p>

Sheffer was first seen on a nationwide basis on the television circuit. He played Ian Hayden on the <network wordnetid="108434259" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../027/62027.xml">
ABC</link></network>
