<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../359/1223359.xml">
That Was Then... This Is Now</link></movie>
</it> (<fundamental_quantity wordnetid="113575869" confidence="0.8">
<time_period wordnetid="115113229" confidence="0.8">
<year wordnetid="115203791" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../615/171615.xml">
1985</link></year>
</time_period>
</fundamental_quantity>
), a reformatory camp inmate in <it><link>
Fire With Fire</link></it>, and an antagonistic rich kid in <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../963/703963.xml">
Some Kind of Wonderful</link></movie>
</it> (<fundamental_quantity wordnetid="113575869" confidence="0.8">
<time_period wordnetid="115113229" confidence="0.8">
<year wordnetid="115203791" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../293/171293.xml">
